<div class="section_create">
    <div class="create">
        <h2 class="blind">카페 만들기</h2>
        <p class="blind">나와 같은 관심사를 가진 멤버를 모집하고 열심히 운영하여 카페를 성장시켜보세요.</p>
    </div>

    <form name="frm" method="post" action="/cafe/create">
            <input type="hidden" name="csKey" value="NTVGbVdQrzG3ICz4" />
            <input type="hidden" name="clubnameck" value="" />
            <input type="hidden" name="cluburlck" value="" />
            <input type="hidden" name="ugcType" value="" />
            <input type="hidden" name="introductionck" value="0" />
            <input type="hidden" name="juniverCafe" value="false" />
